 application that\'s elegant and premium. Users should be able to configure their ideal website: they will select packages, calculate the price, and send their specifications via WhatsApp. I can also build a live mock-up previewer to visualize the final result. All this is planned to run without any external backend dependencies. This looks to be a beautiful user experience.\n\n\n**Expanding Feature Set**\n\nI\'m now identifying additional features to improve user engagement. I\'m focusing on a real-time quote visualizer, where changes dynamically update a responsive \"web mockup preview panel.\" I\'m also thinking of an interactive portfolio showcase with previews and filters, and a responsive order/inquiry drawer. I am thinking through an FAQ section with smooth accordions and an interactive core pages guide. I\'m aiming for a polished design with modern off-white and emerald green styling.\n\n\n"
