    modified_response: "I will create the `/src/components/PricingCalculator.tsx` component. This serves as the major interactive feature of the application: a real-time, custom website builder simulator. It allows users to write their business name, choose category presets, pick from beautiful color themes, configure additional pages, and toggle rich features with instant live preview updates on a simulated mobile-responsive browser canvas. It also features a dynamic pricing breakdown and generates pre-filled WhatsApp links with exact selections."
