  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Professional Polish\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Professional Polish\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-slate-50 flex flex-col overflow-hidden font-sans text-slate-900\\\">\\n  <!-- Navigation -->\\n  <nav class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between px-10 py-6 bg-white border-b border-slate-200\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-white font-bold text-xl\\\">W</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <span class=\\\"font-bold text-2xl tracking-tight text-slate-900\\\">WebPro Digital</span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-8 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600\\\">\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-indigo-700\\\">Layanan</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-indigo-700\\\">Portofolio</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-indigo-700\\\">Tentang Kami</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"px-5 py-2.5 bg-indigo-700 text-white rounded-full hover:bg-indigo-800 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-indigo-200\\\">Konsultasi Gratis</a>\\n    </div>\\n  </nav>\\n\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex px-10 py-8 gap-10\\\">\\n    <!-- Left Content: Hero & Services -->\\n    <div class=\\\"w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n      <section>\\n        <span class=\\\"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4\\\">Solusi Bisnis Digital</span>\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-5xl font-extrabold leading-[1.1] text-slate-900 mb-4\\\">\\n          Website <span class=\\\"text-indigo-700\\\">Profesional</span> untuk Menumbuhkan Bisnis Anda.\\n        </h1>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8 max-w-md leading-relaxed\\\">\\n          Membantu UMKM & Perusahaan membangun kredibilitas online dengan desain modern, cepat, dan responsif.\\n        </p>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex gap-4\\\">\\n          <button class=\\\"px-8 py-4 bg-slate-900 text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-black transition-all shadow-xl\\\">Lihat Paket Website</button>\\n          <button class=\\\"px-8 py-4 border-2 border-slate-200 text-slate-900 font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-white transition-all\\\">Proses Pengerjaan</button>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>\\n\\n      <section class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-8\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"p-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3\\\">\\n            <svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5 text-blue-600\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z\\\"></path></svg>\\n          </div>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"font-bold text-slate-900\\\">Company Profile</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-500 leading-tight mt-1\\\">Ciptakan profil bisnis yang elegan dan terpercaya di mata klien.</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"p-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 bg-green-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3\\\">\\n            <svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5 text-green-600\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M16 11V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4M5 9h14l1 12H4L5 9z\\\"></path></svg>\\n          </div>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"font-bold text-slate-900\\\">E-Commerce</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-500 leading-tight mt-1\\\">Mulai jualan online dengan fitur keranjang & integrasi pembayaran.</p>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Right Content: Pricing & Features -->\\n    <div class=\\\"w-1/2 flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\\\">\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900\\\">Paket Unggulan</h2>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium\\\">Garansi Support Setelah Jadi</span>\\n      </div>\\n      \\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 grid grid-rows-3 gap-4\\\">\\n        <!-- Starter -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 flex items-center justify-between transition-transform hover:border-indigo-300 group\\\">\\n          <div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-indigo-600 bg-indigo-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md uppercase\\\">Starter</span>\\n            <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold mt-1 text-slate-900\\\">Landing Page UMKM</h3>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-500\\\">Mulai dari Rp1.500.000 \342\200\242 7-10 Hari</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase\\\">Fitur Utama</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-600\\\">Responsif \342\200\242 WhatsApp \342\200\242 SEO Basic</div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Business -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-indigo-700 rounded-2xl p-6 flex items-center justify-between shadow-xl shadow-indigo-200 ring-4 ring-indigo-700 ring-offset-2 ring-offset-slate-50\\\">\\n          <div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-white bg-indigo-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md uppercase\\\">Terpopuler</span>\\n            <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold mt-1 text-white\\\">Business Profile</h3>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm text-indigo-100\\\">Mulai dari Rp3.500.000 \342\200\242 14 Hari</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-indigo-300 uppercase\\\">Fitur Lengkap</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"text-xs text-indigo-50\\\">5 Halaman \342\200\242 Maps \342\200\242 Optimasi Speed</div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Custom -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 flex items-center justify-between transition-transform hover:border-indigo-300 group\\\">\\n          <div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 bg-slate-100 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md uppercase\\\">Enterprise</span>\\n            <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold mt-1 text-slate-900\\\">Custom System</h3>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-500\\\">Harga Menyesuaikan Kebutuhan</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase\\\">Layanan Khusus</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-600\\\">Dashboard \342\200\242 Booking \342\200\242 API System</div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Testimonial Mini Card -->\\n      <div class=\\\"mt-6 bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-5 flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-slate-700 flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-white italic\\\">\342\200\234</div>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-300 italic\\\">\\n          \\\"Sekarang calon pelanggan lebih mudah melihat layanan kami dan langsung menghubungi via WhatsApp.\\\"\\n          <span class=\\\"block font-bold text-white not-italic mt-1\\\">\342\200\224 Bpk. Ahmad, UMKM Owner</span>\\n        </p>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </main>\\n\\n  <footer class=\\\"px-10 py-4 bg-white border-t border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-between text-xs text-slate-500\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-6\\\">\\n      <span>\302\251 2026 WebPro Digital Agency</span>\\n      <span>Jl. Sudirman No. 45, Jakarta</span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-6\\\">\\n      <span>WhatsApp: 0812-3456-7890</span>\\n      <span>Email: info@webpro.id</span>\\n      <span class=\\\"font-bold text-indigo-700\\\">Tersedia di Instagram</span>\\n    </div>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Professional Polish\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Professional Polish\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-slate-50 flex flex-col overflow-hidden font-sans text-slate-900\\\">\\n  <!-- Navigation -->\\n  <nav class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between px-10 py-6 bg-white border-b border-slate-200\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-700 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-white font-bold text-xl\\\">W</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <span class=\\\"font-bold text-2xl tracking-tight text-slate-900\\\">WebPro Digital</span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-8 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600\\\">\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-indigo-700\\\">Layanan</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-indigo-700\\\">Portofolio</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-indigo-700\\\">Tentang Kami</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"px-5 py-2.5 bg-indigo-700 text-white rounded-full hover:bg-indigo-800 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-indigo-200\\\">Konsultasi Gratis</a>\\n    </div>\\n  </nav>\\n\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex px-10 py-8 gap-10\\\">\\n    <!-- Left Content: Hero & Services -->\\n    <div class=\\\"w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n      <section>\\n        <span class=\\\"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4\\\">Solusi Bisnis Digital</span>\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-5xl font-extrabold leading-[1.1] text-slate-900 mb-4\\\">\\n          Website <span class=\\\"text-indigo-700\\\">Profesional</span> untuk Menumbuhkan Bisnis Anda.\\n        </h1>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8 max-w-md leading-relaxed\\\">\\n          Membantu UMKM & Perusahaan membangun kredibilitas online dengan desain modern, cepat, dan responsif.\\n        </p>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex gap-4\\\">\\n          <button class=\\\"px-8 py-4 bg-slate-900 text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-black transition-all shadow-xl\\\">Lihat Paket Website</button>\\n          <button class=\\\"px-8 py-4 border-2 border-slate-200 text-slate-900 font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-white transition-all\\\">Proses Pengerjaan</button>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>\\n\\n      <section class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-8\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"p-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3\\\">\\n            <svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5 text-blue-600\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z\\\"></path></svg>\\n          </div>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"font-bold text-slate-900\\\">Company Profile</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-500 leading-tight mt-1\\\">Ciptakan profil bisnis yang elegan dan terpercaya di mata klien.</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"p-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 bg-green-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3\\\">\\n            <svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5 text-green-600\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M16 11V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4M5 9h14l1 12H4L5 9z\\\"></path></svg>\\n          </div>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"font-bold text-slate-900\\\">E-Commerce</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-500 leading-tight mt-1\\\">Mulai jualan online dengan fitur keranjang & integrasi pembayaran.</p>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Right Content: Pricing & Features -->\\n    <div class=\\\"w-1/2 flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\\\">\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900\\\">Paket Unggulan</h2>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium\\\">Garansi Support Setelah Jadi</span>\\n      </div>\\n      \\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 grid grid-rows-3 gap-4\\\">\\n        <!-- Starter -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 flex items-center justify-between transition-transform hover:border-indigo-300 group\\\">\\n          <div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-indigo-600 bg-indigo-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md uppercase\\\">Starter</span>\\n            <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold mt-1 text-slate-900\\\">Landing Page UMKM</h3>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-500\\\">Mulai dari Rp1.500.000 \342\200\242 7-10 Hari</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase\\\">Fitur Utama</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-600\\\">Responsif \342\200\242 WhatsApp \342\200\242 SEO Basic</div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Business -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-indigo-700 rounded-2xl p-6 flex items-center justify-between shadow-xl shadow-indigo-200 ring-4 ring-indigo-700 ring-offset-2 ring-offset-slate-50\\\">\\n          <div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-white bg-indigo-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md uppercase\\\">Terpopuler</span>\\n            <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold mt-1 text-white\\\">Business Profile</h3>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm text-indigo-100\\\">Mulai dari Rp3.500.000 \342\200\242 14 Hari</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-indigo-300 uppercase\\\">Fitur Lengkap</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"text-xs text-indigo-50\\\">5 Halaman \342\200\242 Maps \342\200\242 Optimasi Speed</div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Custom -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-6 flex items-center justify-between transition-transform hover:border-indigo-300 group\\\">\\n          <div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 bg-slate-100 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md uppercase\\\">Enterprise</span>\\n            <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold mt-1 text-slate-900\\\">Custom System</h3>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-500\\\">Harga Menyesuaikan Kebutuhan</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase\\\">Layanan Khusus</div>\\n            <div class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-600\\\">Dashboard \342\200\242 Booking \342\200\242 API System</div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Testimonial Mini Card -->\\n      <div class=\\\"mt-6 bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-5 flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-slate-700 flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-white italic\\\">\342\200\234</div>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-300 italic\\\">\\n          \\\"Sekarang calon pelanggan lebih mudah melihat layanan kami dan langsung menghubungi via WhatsApp.\\\"\\n          <span class=\\\"block font-bold text-white not-italic mt-1\\\">\342\200\224 Bpk. Ahmad, UMKM Owner</span>\\n        </p>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </main>\\n\\n  <footer class=\\\"px-10 py-4 bg-white border-t border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-between text-xs text-slate-500\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-6\\\">\\n      <span>\302\251 2026 WebPro Digital Agency</span>\\n      <span>Jl. Sudirman No. 45, Jakarta</span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-6\\\">\\n      <span>WhatsApp: 0812-3456-7890</span>\\n      <span>Email: info@webpro.id</span>\\n      <span class=\\\"font-bold text-indigo-700\\\">Tersedia di Instagram</span>\\n    </div>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
